{"word":"G3724 - ὁρίζω - horízō - hor-id'-zo - Declare","slug":"G3724","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁρίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>horízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>hor-id'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Declare"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BF;&#x0314;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9; - horizo&#x0304;</b> - <i>hor-id'-zo</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3725\">G3725</a>; to <i>mark</i> out or <i>bound</i> (&ldquo;horizon&rdquo;), that is, (figuratively) to <i>appoint</i>, <i>decree</i>, <i>specify:</i> - declare, determine, limit, ordain."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4309\">G4309</a>, <a href=\"#/G592\">G592</a>, <a href=\"#/G873\">G873</a>"}]}